## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Client["Client Layer (Next.js + PWA)"]
        PWA["PWA Shell<br/>Service Worker + Manifest"]
        APP["Next.js App Router"]
        UI["shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS"]
        STATE["React Query + Zustand"]
        FORMS["React Hook Form + Zod"]
    end

    subgraph Edge["Edge Layer"]
        MW["Next.js Middleware<br/>Auth + Route Protection"]
        EF["Supabase Edge Functions<br/>Complex Business Logic"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Backend Layer (Supabase)"]
        AUTH["Supabase Auth<br/>Email/OAuth"]
        DB["PostgreSQL<br/>+ Row Level Security"]
        STORAGE["Supabase Storage<br/>Attachments/Receipts"]
        RT["Realtime<br/>Live Updates"]
    end

    PWA --> APP
    APP --> UI
    APP --> STATE
    APP --> FORMS
    APP --> MW
    MW --> AUTH
    STATE --> DB
    STATE --> RT
    EF --> DB
    FORMS --> EF
    APP --> STORAGE
```

### Layered Architecture

| Layer | Technology | Responsibility |
|-------|-----------|----------------|
| **Presentation** | Next.js App Router, React, Tailwind, shadcn/ui | UI rendering, routing, forms |
| **State Management** | TanStack Query + Zustand | Server state caching, client state |
| **Validation** | Zod + React Hook Form | Client & server-side validation |
| **API** | Supabase Client SDK + Edge Functions | Data access, business logic |
| **Auth** | Supabase Auth + Next.js Middleware | Authentication, session management |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL + RLS | Data persistence, security |
| **Storage** | Supabase Storage | File uploads (receipts, PDFs) |
| **Offline** | Service Worker + IndexedDB | PWA offline support, sync queue |

