## Phase Breakdown

| Phase | Name | Modules | Est. Duration |
|-------|------|---------|---------------|
| **1** | Foundation & Infrastructure | Project setup, Auth, Layout, Design System, PWA, DB foundation | ~3 days |
| **2** | Expense Tracking | Categories, Transactions, Recurring, Attachments, CSV import/export | ~3 days |
| **3** | Income & Salary Tracking | Income sources, Salary components, Appraisal history | ~2 days |
| **4** | Investment Tracking | Portfolio, Asset types, CAGR/XIRR calculations, Net worth | ~3 days |
| **5** | Goals & Milestones | Goal CRUD, Linked investments, Progress tracking, Milestones | ~2 days |
| **6** | Notes & Timeline | Markdown editor, Attachments, Chronological timeline | ~2 days |
| **7** | Analytics & Reports | Interactive dashboards, Charts, Export, Date range analysis | ~3 days |
| **8** | Polish & Production | Offline sync, Performance, Testing, Deployment | ~2 days |

> Each phase follows: **Schema → Migrations → APIs → UI → Tests → Review**

